OL,3,CWelsh Government minister behind 20mph
OL,4,C'hopes' some roads will go back to
OL,5,C30mph
OL,7,FThe minister behind has said he
OL,8,F"hopes" some roads will return to
OL,9,F30mph following a review.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Wales' programme on
OL,12,FMonday (29 January) deputy climate
OL,13,Fchange minister Lee Waters explained
OL,14,Fcouncils had initially been "very
OL,15,Fnervous" to keep roads at a higher
OL,16,Fspeed limit but will now be given
OL,17,F"encouragement" to do so where
OL,18,Fsuitable.
