OL,3,CWelsh Government minister behind 20mph
OL,4,C'hopes' some roads will go back to
OL,5,C30mph
OL,7,FIn his role in the, Mr Waters was
OL,8,Finstrumental in introducing the
OL,9,Fcontroversial law in September last
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FIt meant Wales became the first UK
OL,13,Fnation to decrease the default speed
OL,14,Flimit to 20mph.
OL,16,FLee Waters told ITV Wales' Sharp End
OL,17,Fcouncils had initially been "very
OL,18,Fnervous" to deviate from 20mph but he
OL,19,Fhopes they will be more confident to
OL,20,Freturn roads to 30mph where suitable
OL,21,Ffollowing the review.
