OL,7,FThere has been some confusion about
OL,8,Fwhich roads it applies to, as well as
OL,9,Fhow it is enforced, .
OL,11,FMr Waters told Rob Osborne the rule
OL,12,Fchange was "the biggest change to the
OL,13,Frules of the road in over a
OL,14,Fgeneration," and was "not going to be
OL,15,Fperfect on day one."
OL,17,FA review is now underway to look at
OL,18,Fhow it has been implemented, as well
OL,19,Fas its effectiveness so far.
