OL,7,FHe said Wales' 22 councils had taken
OL,8,F"different approaches" to the changing
OL,9,Fregulations and admitted "there are
OL,10,Fsome problems that we need to iron
OL,11,Fout."
OL,13,FMr Waters added: "To be fair to
OL,14,Fcouncils, some of these judgements are
OL,15,Fnot black and white."
