OL,7,FAnother 30% thought about leaving
OL,8,Ftheir job after receiving threats or
OL,9,Fabuse.
OL,11,FWhen asked about abuse he has faced
OL,12,Fafter the introduction of 20mph, Mr
OL,13,FWaters said he had recently blocked
OL,14,Fpeople on social media - something he
OL,15,Fhas not done before - because the
OL,16,F"tsunami" of negative comments had
OL,17,Fbeen "overwhelming" for his mental
OL,18,Fhealth.
